"$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"高高的天线两侧，电波在飞鸣，"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"密集的弹雨折不断电波的矫健翅翎；"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"为了胜利，"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"穿过西北战场的硝烟，"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"不倦地飞呀，飞向广阔的天宇。"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"恍惚中，她自己也化为一道金黑的电波了，"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"像海燕在陌生的瀚海上空驰骋；"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"她微笑着，"}],["$","p","21",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"她睡熟了，"}],["$","p","22",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"安详而且宁静。"}],["$","p","23",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","24",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","准噶尔诗草","》 · ","卷之二：将军与城"]}],["$","span",null,{"children":["页码 ","31"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["李瑜"," / ","1984年"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-2-3","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"普罗米修斯点燃了沉沉夜幕"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"一星火光闪耀着，"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"召唤看不见的铁流径直向西；"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"战士迈开铁脚，"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"踏在遥远的异域，"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"踏在神秘的异域。"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"这是曾闪耀丝绸光泽的大地，"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"这是曾摇曳燃烧红柳的大地，"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"曾飘浮戈壁之舟的点点帆影的大地，"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"曾摇曳叮冬驼铃的轻柔夜曲的大地。"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"褐黄的天穹此刻是墨黑的，"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"褐黄的大漠此刻也是墨黑的，"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":["戎马佐您的",["$","span","1",{"className":"annotation-term border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 cursor-help","title":"古希腊神话中盗取天火给人类的泰坦神。此处诗人以此比喻在新疆为革命献身的先驱者，他们如同盗火者，为黑暗中的人们带来光明与希望。","children":["普罗米修斯",["$","sup",null,{"className":"text-xs text-gray-400 ml-px select-none","children":1}]]}],"点燃沉沉夜幕，"]}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"也将点燃天山下带露的晨曦。"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"将军跃马沙包，"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"手中的那根火柴熄灭了，"}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"一星火光消逝了；"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"大军又都沉浸在混沌黑暗之中，"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"瀚海彼岸上那片鱼肚白已泛起在脑际。"}],["$","p","21",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","22",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-xs font-sans font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4","children":"注释"}],["$","ol",null,{"className":"space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"flex text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"cla