ldren":"未来的新城在哪儿呢？"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"褐色的地平线依然在瀚海飘摇，"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"褐色的地平线依然还那么遥远。"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"浑圆的落日滚进山峦般起伏的沙包，"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"收回刚刚射出的最后一支灿烂金箭；"}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"夜呀夜呀，"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"夜幕快些降临吧，"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"只有穿过黑夜才能达到铺满晨曦的绿洲。"}],["$","p","21",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","22",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","准噶尔诗草","》 · ","卷之二：将军与城"]}],["$","span",null,{"children":["页码 ","33"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["李瑜"," / ","1984年"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-2-5","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"匆匆从远方来"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"匆匆从远方来，"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"铁骑切开了巍巍沙包，"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"像飞翔在凝固了的波涛上的一只山鹰。"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"给古老的西域留下了什么呢？"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"给未来的新城留下了什么呢？"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"将军回过头去，"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"遥遥地眺望，"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"笑指一路撒下的彩虹般的花纹。"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"穿过神州的万条阔水，"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"穿过神州的千条山岭，"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"穿过海涛般的钢铁交响。"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"穿过褐黄的大漠，"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"穿过褐黄的浮云。"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"匆匆到远方去，"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在马背上为了追寻憧憬的圣地，"}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"从子夜走到黎明……"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","准噶尔诗草","》 · ","卷之二：将军与城"]}],["$","span",null,{"children":["页码 ","34"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["李瑜"," / ","1984年"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-2-6","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"流淌着一条翡翠的小河"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"曳着呼啸的浪，"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"曳着闪光的波；"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在那巍峨沙包的山峰间，"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在那灰褐风沙的雾霭里，"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"流淌着一条翡翠的小河。"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"簇拥着层层叠叠的浪花，"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在夕阳照映下奔腾着，喧哗着，"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"她的涛声就是大地轻轻的呼吸，"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"那么妩媚，"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"那么柔和。"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"不息地浅吟呀，"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"不息地低唱呀，"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"将瘦小野花苍白的脸儿唱酡，"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"将美丽云霞苍白的脸儿唱酡，"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"将浑圆落日苍白的脸儿唱酡。"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"开拓者趁着梦幻般的黎明，"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"映着硝烟，映着烽火，"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在这儿植下了一条翡翠般的林带，"}],["$","p","21",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"——这条翡翠的小河就这样流进"}],["$","p","22",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"褐色的大漠，"}],["$","p","23",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"流进未来的新城，唱着欢歌。"}],["$","p","24",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","25",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","准噶尔诗草","》 · ","卷之二：将军与城"]}],["$","span",null,{"children":["页码 ","35"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["李瑜"," / ","1984年"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-2-7","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"那梦幻中向往的生命的乐土"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"哪儿来的楼阁在眼前漂浮，"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"哪儿来的水榭在眼前漂浮；"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在弥漫硝烟的沙包上苏醒过来了，"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"双手还紧攥炙热的沙砾一抓，"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"褐色的风沙线上出现一片葱茏的绿洲，"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"——那梦幻中向往的生命的乐土；"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"掩映一弯清水，"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"竖立千丛碧树。"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"那边饱和雨水的云块缓缓飘来，"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"晶莹的云块还簇拥轻纱般的薄雾；"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"飘过来了，飘过来了，"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"连风儿也湿漉漉。"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"凝固的沙浪又在眼前飘浮，"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"燃烧的红柳又在眼前飘浮；"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"神奇的海市蜃楼霎时从迷惘的瞳孔里隐去了，"}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"可是，褐色的风沙线哪能阻挡他的脚步。"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"child