，"}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"一座新城就耸立心坎，"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"庄严而且巍峨；"}],["$","p","21",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在褐色大漠植下第一条青青的林带，"}],["$","p","22",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":["趁着西北战场的黎明筑起这道翡翠的",["$","span","1",{"className":"annotation-term border-b border-dotted border-gray-400 cursor-help","title":"城墙上的矮墙。此处「翡翠的城垛」象征军垦战士在戈壁上建起的绿色家园——用开荒造林筑成的绿色屏障。","children":["城垛",["$","sup",null,{"className":"text-xs text-gray-400 ml-px select-none","children":1}]]}],"。"]}],["$","p","23",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","24",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100","children":[["$","h4",null,{"className":"text-xs font-sans font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4","children":"注释"}],["$","ol",null,{"className":"space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"flex text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"text-xs text-gray-400 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0 font-mono","children":[1,"."]}],["$","span",null,{"children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-medium text-gray-600","children":"城垛"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"mx-1.5 text-gray-300","children":"—"}],"城墙上的矮墙。此处「翡翠的城垛」象征军垦战士在戈壁上建起的绿色家园——用开荒造林筑成的绿色屏障。"]}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","准噶尔诗草","》 · ","卷之二：将军与城"]}],["$","span",null,{"children":["页码 ","38"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["李瑜"," / ","1984年"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-2-10","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"象火中再生的美丽凤凰"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"笔直的林带，"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"笔直的小径，"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"笔直的水渠，"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"笔直的通衢；"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"谁知未来新城蓝图上经经纬纬笔直的线"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"却是老兵瞄着机枪的准星测绘成的。"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"乌云已经消散了，"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"黑夜已经逝去了，"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"请不要忘记，"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"——请以革命的名义；"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"未来新城就像火中再生的美丽凤凰，"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"将从弥漫的硝烟中振翅飞起……"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-gray-500 font-sans","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":["《","准噶尔诗草","》 · ","卷之二：将军与城"]}],["$","span",null,{"children":["页码 ","39"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-xs text-gray-400 text-center","children":["李瑜"," / ","1984年"]}]]}]]}],["$","article",null,{"id":"poem-2-11","className":"max-w-2xl mx-auto py-32 px-8 scroll-mt-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-16","children":["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-serif leading-relaxed","children":"绿色的箭在飞驰"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-1 font-serif text-xl text-gray-800 leading-[2.2]","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"迎着瀚海滚滚浪涛，"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"一支绿色的箭在飞驰，"}],["$","p","2",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在茫茫的天宇闪耀，"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在褐黄的天宇闪耀；"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"紧贴大漠不倦地向前飞去，"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"一位老兵的豪情还在修长的箭翎上高挑。"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","7",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"这支箭穿过大西北飘散的硝烟，"}],["$","p","8",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"迎着漠风，呜呜嘶叫，"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"向往那为之奋斗的春晓；"}],["$","p","10",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"穿过红柳的璀璨纱帐，"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"穿过波涛的澄黄浮雕。"}],["$","p","12",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","13",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"还穿过水榭，"}],["$","p","14",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"还穿过楼台，"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"缥缈的海市蜃楼哪有心中的憧憬妖娆；"}],["$","p","16",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在前方，在那遥远的风沙线上，"}],["$","p","17",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"参差的沙包还在轻轻飘摇。"}],["$","p","18",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","19",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"绿色的箭"}],["$","p","20",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"——那刚刚种植的林带，"}],["$","p","21",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"不倦地向前飞去，百折不挠，"}],["$","p","22",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"还曳着辛辣的莫合烟的雾云袅袅；"}],["$","p","23",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"呼啸着，射向暴虐的沙龙，"}],["$","p","24",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"在漫长的途中孕育绿色的狂飙。"}],["$","p","25",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] h-6","children":""}],["$","p","26",{"className":"min-h-[1.5em] ","children":"1979年7月"}]]}],false,["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-20 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex justify-between items-center tex